            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="category-card h-100 text-center p-4">
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Sună-ne</h3>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Departament Vânzări:</strong><br>0720 123 456</p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Serviciu Clienți:</strong><br>0730 789 012</p>
